{"tid":220362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（宇宙大王呀）【金仔靠嚇】北韓青年團誓言 500萬人配核彈保護金正恩","createTime":"2017-04-28T01:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T01:58:46.000Z","uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba184f39b8b6dd0b3cb787b8d7488aa2a7403041","tid":220362,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:50:06.000Z","msg":"朝鮮半島局勢緊張，北韓有青年團誓言為保家衞國，就算粉身碎骨也在所不辭，表示有500萬名青年會「配備核彈無情地殲滅」美國及南韓等敵人。<br />\n<br />\n「金日成及金正日社會主義青年同盟」發聲明表示，北韓青少年的決心是「堅定及無情地剷除美國帝國主義和南韓傀儡」，他們的成員會以「無敵核力量」打擊敵人，誓言「消滅地球上的所有侵略者和挑釁者」，到最終會放煙花慶祝勝利。<br />\n<br />\n青年團強調：「美國帝國主義者要知道，如果（北韓釋放）無敵核力量，以及裝備核彈的500萬年輕人發怒的話，地球將會爆裂。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56620175&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56620175%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170427&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b72abdbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56620175%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170427&h=cc85c19b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56620175&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170427</a>"},{"pid":"d1869017c420f1ef6b63a3ee74799949790cfb3d","tid":220362,"uid":14091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:53:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n青年團強調：「美國帝國主義者要知道，如果（北韓釋放）無敵核力量，以及裝備核彈的500萬年輕人發怒的話，<span style=\"color: red;\">地球將會爆裂</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f729b7bb1408213dbf121191bcc47dce85fd66","tid":220362,"uid":36378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:57:36.000Z","msg":"爆裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93aaed3ba6bcc98ae6abb2b9d478066423d180c","tid":220362,"uid":71342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:58:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n青年團強調：「美國帝國主義者要知道，如果（北韓釋放）無敵核力量，以及裝備核彈的500萬年輕人發怒的話，<span style=\"color: red;\">地球將會爆裂</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係條肥恩太肥，踩爆瑰地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}